Time is running out for entries into the Nashua Loskop Marathon and Wild Challenge and runners have until 17 March to register! The Loskop Marathon, now sponsored by Nashua, will include a 50 km Comrades qualifier from Middelburg to Loskop Dam Forever Resorts as well as the much-loved 21 km Wild Challenge through the Loskop Nature Reserve. Participants are urged to enter before this coming Friday by visiting the Middelburg Marathon Club (in person), or alternatively by visiting loskop@peaktiming.co.za. For more information, contact 061 919 1003. 